data.title: List of Correspondents 2021
data.meta_description: Gard_Correspondents_December2021 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists contact details for Gard P&I correspondents and claims handlers, including mobile phone numbers to call outside office hours. It provides the names, titles and mobile phone numbers of over 50 claims executives and leaders within the Gard organization who can be contacted for assistance in urgent matters. The correspondents are organized by location and specialty, including People Claims, Dry Cargo Claims, Casualty Claims, Marine Claims, and P&I and Offshore Energy Claims.
